      "blocks": {
        "mention_1": {
          "type": "mention",
          "settings": {
            "product": "r8-foldable-exercise-bike-magnetic-resistance",
            "text": "<p>The Ativafit Folding Magnetic Exercise Bike is an affordable and efficient bike. It's smooth, quiet, and offers a range of eight adjustable magnetic resistance levels for variability when training. </p>",
            "link": "https://www.garagegymreviews.com/equipment/ativafit-folding-magnetic-exercise-bike",
            "logo": "shopify://shop_images/garage_review_2081e3bb-bd05-4a3f-8931-d19950655a05.webp",
            "logo_asset": "ggr-new-site-logo.png",
            "logo_bg": false
          }
        },
        "mention_2": {
          "type": "mention",
          "settings": {
            "product": "f8-foldable-exercise-bike",
            "text": "<p>The Ativafit R8 offers a powerful punch for a small price tag. We enjoyed the great workout that this small but robust cycle offered, allowing riders to select their preferred riding position and integrate resistance training into their workout. </p>",
            "link": "https://indoorcyclinglove.com/ativafit-r8-foldable-exercise-bike",
            "logo_asset": "Indoor-Cycling-Love-FF-3-01.webp",
            "logo_bg": false
          }
        }
      },
