    "image_tabs_bike": {
      "type": "image-tabs",
      "blocks": {
        "tab_bike_2": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Comfort for Every Rider",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/bike_feature2.webp",
            "text": "<p>Our collection offers versatile fitness solutions to meet different workout preferences. The F8 features a traditional upright riding position for a classic cycling experience, while the R8 provides a flexible 2-in-1 folding exercise bike design that can function as both an upright and semi-recumbent bike.Both models are built for durability and stability. The R8 also includes a supportive backrest, making it a comfortable exercise bike for seniors or anyone looking for a low-impact workout that is easier on the joints.</p>"
          }
        },
        "tab_bike_3": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Smooth Magnetic Resistance",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/5_c7df0068-b1f6-4031-8449-28d980c41870.webp",
            "text": "<p>Enjoy quiet and consistent workouts with our advanced magnetic resistance system. Multiple resistance levels allow you to adjust intensity from light recovery rides to challenging cardio sessions on a foldable gym cycle.The whisper-quiet design means you can exercise anytime without disturbing others in your home.</p>"
          }
        },
        "tab_bike_1": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Foldable & Space-Saving",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/bike_feature.webp",
            "text": "<p>One of the biggest advantages of an Ativafit foldable exercise bike is its compact design. Both the F8 and R8 models feature an exercise bike foldaway structure that allows the bike to collapse quickly after your workout.This makes them ideal for apartments, small home gyms, or shared living spaces where a full-size foldable stationary bike might otherwise take up too much room.</p>"
          }
        },
        "tab_bike_4": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Track Your Workout",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/OPTIMIZE_BACKUP_PRODUCT_F8FoldableExerciseBikew.HealthMonitor-Ativafit_5.png",
            "text": "<p>Both the F8 and R8 are equipped with a digital monitor that displays key workout metrics in real time, including time, distance, speed, and calories burned.For a more complete training experience, the R8 also includes built-in resistance bands so you can combine upper-body movements with your exercise cycle foldable workout routine.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "tab_bike_2",
        "tab_bike_3",
        "tab_bike_1",
        "tab_bike_4"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "padding_top": 24,
        "padding_bottom": 24
      }
    },
